title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Throwing Bits
description:
Like we always do at this time, the Core 4 are linking up for what technically could be described as the Jüicy Zöömy after after party and the conversation is flowing like ice cold Bud heavies because beer is back. Topics include, but are not limited to: James’ strategic pivot, our latest “live” show recap, newsletter drama, Virgil Abloh vs. Four Pins, Fashion’s reckoning, ’The Proposition’ (2005), the new sneaker hierarchy, Larry smoking weed again and much more for our extremely tasteful best friends behind the paywall.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
